### =============================================
### ADMIN - AUTH (LOGIN)
### =============================================

### Login válido (Diretor, todas permissões)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "joao.silva",
  "senha": "123"
}

### Login válido (Admin TI)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "marcos.rocha",
  "senha": "123"
}

### Login válido (Engenheiro, permissões limitadas)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "carlos.lima",
  "senha": "123"
}

### Senha errada → 401
POST {{host}}/api/admin/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "joao.silva",
  "senha": "senhaerrada"
}

### Usuário inexistente → 401
POST {{host}}/api/admin/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "naoexiste",
  "senha": "qualquer"
}

### Campos vazios → 401
POST {{host}}/api/admin/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "",
  "senha": ""
}
